Kani waa '''template gumud'''.  Sharaxad kooban oo ku saabsan template kaan; faahfaahin dhameestiran ka fiiri [[Wikipedia:Gumud]]. 

===Waa maxay gumud?===
Gumud waa maqaal ee ku jiraan qoraalo  yar, oo ah kuwo aad u gaaban oo dabooli karin maadooyinka encyclopediyaha.

===Sidee jir loo aqoonsadaa?===
*Haddii ay suurtagal tahay, isku day inaad u hesho templateka ugu habboon ee maqaalka. Liis buuxa waxaa laga heli karaa [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Stub sorting/Stub types]].
*Labo ama in ka badan oo template kala duwan ah ayaa loo isticmaali karaa, haddii loo baahdo,  in kastoo aan ka badnayn afar waa in loo adeegsadaa maqaal kasta.
*Dhig templateka gumud maqaalka ''[[WP:FOOTERS|meesha ugu hooseeso]]''  kadib qaybaha "linkyada dheeraadka", Sida caadiga ah, templateyada waxaa lagu daraa iyadoo lagu daray magacyadooda gudaha laba laab, tusaale {{stub}}., e.g. <nowiki>{{stub}}</nowiki>.

===Faahfaahin dheeri ah===
Faahfaahin dheeri ah waxaa  ka heli kartaa:
*[[Wikipedia:Stub]]
*[[Wikipedia:WikiProject Stub sorting]]

New stub templates and categories (collectively "stub types") should not be created without prior proposal at [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Stub sorting/Proposals]]. This allows for the proper coordination of all stub types across Wikipedia, and for the checking of any new stub type for possible problems prior to its creation.

